snippet.title: Play the Wind's Path! Available on Steam
snippet.description:
The Top Down Platformer is available for Steam!

Play on Steam:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2424500/The_Winds_Path/

The Wind's Path is a top-down #platformer #indiegame I'm making with the #godotengine

#gameplay running on the #SteamDeck 

Itch.io
https://endless-project.itch.io/winds-path
